Compare South Beach Diet to Atkins

On the South Beach Diet, you'll lose weight with plenty of lean protein and heart-healthy good fats that nourish and satisfy—an approach that literally turns off the switch for sugar and refined-carb cravings.
Atkins' approach heavily restricts carbs and their packaged foods are higher in sodium and saturated fat.
 View Plan 








South Beach Diet: Less Saturated Fat, Less Sodium, More Taste. You Decide.





