Lose Weight and Live a Heart-Healthy Life Without Hunger or Deprivation.
The South Beach Diet, created by world-renowned cardiologist Dr. Agatston, incorporates heart-healthy, unsaturated fats like olive oil, avocado, and nuts, in place of unhealthy fats. These “good fats” will help you lose weight fast without being hungry.








Enjoy Delicious Meals and More Variety with the South Beach Diet.
With a wide variety of fully prepared meals, the South Beach Diet offers hearty, delicious breakfasts, lunch and dinner entr�es, and savory or sweet snacks in a range of globally inspired flavors. Enjoy a different dish each meal without growing tired of eating the same old thing. You won't be limited to just bars, shakes, and a handful of prepared meals like you are on Atkins.










